            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729932",
        "quote": "Abolitionists believe that, as all men are born free, so all who are now held as slaves in this country were born free, and that they are slaves now is the sin, not of those who introduced the race into this country, but of those, and those alone, who now hold them and have held them in slavery from their birth.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729932"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Believe",
                "url": "/topics/believe"
            },
            {
                "name": "Country",
                "url": "/topics/country"
            },
            {
                "name": "Held",
                "url": "/topics/held"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729914",
        "quote": "I was, by divine grace, enabled to bring all my sins and all my sorrows and lay them at the feet of Jesus, and to receive the blessed assurance that He had accepted me, all sinful and polluted as I was.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729914"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Feet",
                "url": "/topics/feet"
            },
            {
                "name": "Lay",
                "url": "/topics/lay"
            },
            {
                "name": "Receive",
                "url": "/topics/receive"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729926",
        "quote": "As long as I am an American citizen, and as long as American blood runs in these veins, I shall hold myself at liberty to speak, to write, and to publish whatever I please on any subject, being amenable to the laws of my country for the same.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729926"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Country",
                "url": "/topics/country"
            },
            {
                "name": "Subject",
                "url": "/topics/subject"
            },
            {
                "name": "Amenable",
                "url": "/topics/amenable"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729922",
        "quote": "The cry of the oppressed has entered not only into my ears, but into my soul, so that while I live, I cannot hold my peace.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729922"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Soul",
                "url": "/topics/soul"
            },
            {
                "name": "Cry",
                "url": "/topics/cry"
            },
            {
                "name": "Entered",
                "url": "/topics/entered"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729923",
        "quote": "I have sworn eternal opposition to slavery, and by the blessing of God, I will never go back.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729923"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Opposition",
                "url": "/topics/opposition"
            },
            {
                "name": "Never",
                "url": "/topics/never"
            },
            {
                "name": "Eternal",
                "url": "/topics/eternal"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729936",
        "quote": "While I value the good opinion of my fellow citizens as highly as anyone, I may be permitted to say that I am governed by higher considerations than either the favor or the fear of man. I am impelled to the course I have taken because I fear God.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729936"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Good",
                "url": "/topics/good"
            },
            {
                "name": "While",
                "url": "/topics/while"
            },
            {
                "name": "Either",
                "url": "/topics/either"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729933",
        "quote": "Emancipation - what is meant by it? Simply that the slaves shall cease to be held as property and shall henceforth be held and treated as human beings. Simply, that we should take our feet from off their necks.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729933"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Slaves",
                "url": "/topics/slaves"
            },
            {
                "name": "Emancipation",
                "url": "/topics/emancipation"
            },
            {
                "name": "Meant",
                "url": "/topics/meant"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729929",
        "quote": "Truth is eternal, unchanging, though circumstances may and do operate to give a different colour to it, in our view, at different times. And truth will prevail, and those who do not yield to it must be destroyed by it.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729929"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Circumstances",
                "url": "/topics/circumstances"
            },
            {
                "name": "Give",
                "url": "/topics/give"
            },
            {
                "name": "Though",
                "url": "/topics/though"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729937",
        "quote": "If I have been guilty of no violation of law, why am I hunted up and down continually like a partridge upon the mountains? Why am I threatened with the tar barrel? Why am I waylaid every day, and from night to night, and my life in jeopardy every hour?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729937"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mountains",
                "url": "/topics/mountains"
            },
            {
                "name": "My Life",
                "url": "/topics/my_life"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729928",
        "quote": "If I know my own heart, I do now feel the necessity of resigning myself into the hands of my God, to mould and guide me at His will; tho I dare not say that I am, at present, willing to do it.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729928"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Hands",
                "url": "/topics/hands"
            },
            {
                "name": "Own",
                "url": "/topics/own"
            },
            {
                "name": "Willing",
                "url": "/topics/willing"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729927",
        "quote": "The very flag of freedom that waves over our heads is formed from material cultivated by slaves, on soil moistened with their blood drawn from them by the whip of a republican taskmaster!",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729927"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Waves",
                "url": "/topics/waves"
