                "url": "/topics/like"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729917",
        "quote": "The eternal God - the infinite Jehovah - has done all he could do - even to the sacrificing his own Son - to provide a way for man's happiness, and yet they reject him, hate him, and laugh him to scorn!",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729917"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Infinite",
                "url": "/topics/infinite"
            },
            {
                "name": "Jehovah",
                "url": "/topics/jehovah"
            },
            {
                "name": "Could",
                "url": "/topics/could"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729910",
        "quote": "Fortune has, in the main, hitherto looked unfavourably upon me since I left home, but I begin to hope for better things. Still, in all my past distresses, one thought has consoled me - I have learned to appreciate a parent's love.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729910"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Thought",
                "url": "/topics/thought"
            },
            {
                "name": "Parent",
                "url": "/topics/parent"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729915",
        "quote": "Nothing but a miracle of sovereign mercy could have arrested and saved me from eternal perdition. How I could have so long resisted the entreaties, the prayers, and the tears of my dear parents, and the influences of the Holy Spirit, is, to me, a wonder entirely incomprehensible.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729915"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Tears",
                "url": "/topics/tears"
            },
