                "url": "/topics/subject"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729913",
        "quote": "It seems to me scarcely possible that one who has so long lived in sin, who has resisted so much light and has so often grieved away the Holy Spirit, as I have, should again be visited with its heavenly influences. But I hope it is so.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729913"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Hope",
