                "url": "/topics/easiest_thing"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729918",
        "quote": "I am sure I ought not to be, but I have great reason to tremble lest Satan and my own wicked heart get the better of me. It is no easy matter to fight such enemies as these, but with Christ strengthening me, I know I shall come off more than a conquerer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729918"
        },
        "topics": [
