    {
        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729920",
        "quote": "I cannot surrender my principles, though the whole world besides should vote them down - I can make no compromise between truth and error, even though my life be the alternative.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729920"
        },
