        "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729921",
        "quote": "I have appealed to the constitution and laws of my country; if they fail to protect me, I appeal to God, and with Him I cheerfully rest my cause. I can die at my post, but I cannot desert it.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Elijah Parish Lovejoy",
            "url": "/quotes/elijah_parish_lovejoy_729921"
